{
 "name": "RPlog_TCF_is_Born",
 "title": "The Tracer Containment Fund is Born",
 "summary": "In the Swoops n' More shop at the Black Krayt Swoop Arena, the Imperial intelligence operative Joir -- traveling under a Sienar Fleet Systems sponsorship cover and flanked by two imposing bodyguards -- pays a visit to the nervous Rodian shopkeeper Bochek. Joir notes that Bochek has been expanding into the weapons trade on Bespin and, after a tense exchange designed to intimidate, hands over a credit chip of eight thousand credits to fund their arrangement. The frightened Bochek accepts the payment gratefully and confirms their continued cooperation. Joir departs with a contemptuous parting reminder in Rodian, sealing a covert financial relationship that will support his interests on Bespin.",
